{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ec91522d1","title":"紧急声明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1fad68a39b","index":0,"year":1938,"month":6,"day":3,"articleId":"5ec91522d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"39eacbb3e3","type":"paragraph","text":"紧急声明","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"5ec91522d1"},{"id":"496ab0ca5b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年6月3日）项闻中央社重庆电，中国国民党监察委员会三日上午八时开十四次常会通过恢复陈其玻等二十六人党籍一案内列有周恩来、林箱涵、吴玉章、毛泽东、童必武、邓额超、叶剑英等七人姓名。按部人等系中国共产党党员，国共两党虽在政治上已告合作，但组织上两党合作关系是否恢复民国十三年之办法井未商定，而对恢复部人等国民党党籍，事前更未通知与征求本党中央及部人等意见，因特郑重声明：中国国民党中央监委此项决议关系部人等七人部分，部人等实不能承认","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"5ec91522d1"},{"id":"0a4c8bf736","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来林祖涵吴玉章毛泽东董必武邓颖超叶剑英同启","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"5ec91522d1"}],"page":{"id":"4286169598","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"5ec91522d1","start":346,"end":346}}}},"__N_SSG":true}